t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">810058484741</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DOUBLE ENDED PICK SET - ToolTreaux set of wax carvers features 4 different double-sided pick tools for a variety of crafting uses like carving, picking, sculpting, jewelry making, make up and special effects. 8 different tips make up the ultimate set of multi-tools for any crafting project requiring precision work</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - Wax carver spatulas are made of high-quality stainless steel that won’t rust, making it ideal for use with both wet and dry mediums. Corrosion-resistant material ensures a long life for your tools</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">VERSATILE CRAFTING TOOLS - Originally designed for precision work, these craft-specific pick tools are great for carving wax, cleaning small parts, creating designs, molding, modeling, and smoothing. Ideal mediums: ceramics, jewelry, clay and electronics</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">KNURLED HANDLES - Featuring ergonomic knurled handles, these tools are shaped for balance and comfort to prevent slippage during use. Measuring 8” in length, entire set will easily fit inside most standard tool boxes and craft storage containers</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS - 4pc set; Assorted tips: 8 (double-sided); Material: stainless steel: Handle style: knurled ergonomic grip: Dimensions: 8” x .6” x .6”; Color: chrome; PVC storage pouch included</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ToolTreaux Stainless Steel Double Ended Knurled Picks Hobby Craft Tools - 4pc</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">13.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>The ToolTreaux deluxe set of wax carvers features 4 different double-ended spatula tools for a variety of crafting uses like sculpting, carving, picking, jewelry making, make up special effects and more. Each set comes with 8 assorted tips that make the ultimate set of multi-tools for precision work crafting projects.\n\nThese spatula tools are constructed of durable, high-quality stainless steel that won’t rust, making them ideal for use with both wet and dry mediums. The corrosion-resistant material will ensure a long life for your tools (just make sure to wipe them clean and dry them before you put them away).\n\nOriginally designed for precision work, these craft-specific pick tools are great for cleaning small parts, carving wax, creating designs, modeling, molding and smoothing. Some recommended mediums for spatula pick tools are ceramics, jewelry and clay. \n\nFeaturing gripped handles, these tools are shaped for comfort and balance to prevent slippage during use, protecting your hands from the picks. Each tool measures about 8” in length, and the entire set will easily fit inside most standard tool boxes and craft storage containers. We’ve also included a PVC storage pouch to keep them all safe and organized when not in use.</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t<table>&nbsp;</table>\n\t</div>\n</body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=0 width=88 height=33 src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_poweredby-en.gif\"></a></center>",
